title: BTS, Border Crossing/Entry Data, United States, 2006
name: BTS, Border Crossing/Entry Data, United States, 2006
description:
Incoming border crossing/entry data 2006 for vehicles, containers, passengers and pedestrians. The data represents activity at the port level on the U.S.-Canadian and U.S.-Mexican land border and international ferry crossings. The data is provided to BTS by the U.S. Department of Homeland Security - Customs and Border Protection

Missing and/or Null values were filled with -1
